velopment of the pulmonary infundibulum and its sequelae. <em>Am J Cardiol</em> 1970;26(1):25–33.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/0002-9149(70)90754-X">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/5427829/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Tetralogy+of+Fallot%3A+underdevelopment+of+the+pulmonary+infundibulum+and+its+sequelae&amp;author=R+Van+Praagh&amp;author=S+Van+Praagh&amp;author=RA+Nebesar&amp;author=AJ+Muster&amp;author=SN+Sinha&amp;author=MH+Paul&amp;publication_year=1970&amp;journal=Am+J+Cardiol&amp;pages=25-33&amp;doi=10.1016%2F0002-9149%2870%2990754-X&amp;pmid=5427829">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Anderson RH, Allwork SP, Ho SY, Lenox CC, Zuberbuhler JR. Surgical anatomy of tetralogy of Fallot. <em>J Thorac Cardiovasc Surg</em> 1981;81(6):887–896.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0022-5223(19)39424-3">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7194951/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Surgical+anatomy+of+tetralogy+of+Fallot&amp;author=RH+Anderson&amp;author=SP+Allwork&amp;author=SY+Ho&amp;author=CC+Lenox&amp;author=JR+Zuberbuhler&amp;publication_year=1981&amp;journal=J+Thorac+Cardiovasc+Surg&amp;pages=887-896&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0022-5223%2819%2939424-3&amp;pmid=7194951">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">13.</div><div id="r13" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Pigula FA, Khalil PN, Mayer JE, del Nido PJ, Jonas